title: Proceed?
message: Do you want me to run this verification plan now without making code changes?
controls:
- option: verification_approval | Run verification (Recommended) | I will execute the non-mutating tests/capture and report results only.
- option: verification_approval | Revise plan | I will adjust the plan before running anything.
- option: verification_approval | Hold off | I will stop here and make no further checks.
